sted I am sure has increased effects... has a WIS + when the charm requires mana and is most assuredly INT based.  The Nostrolo's Tambourine provides +5 INT...<br><br>/em shrug<br><br>I can only guess, considering that many of the wind instrument based songs involve some sort of control over the mind, that perhaps wisdom may have some effect, but again only a guess.<br><br>I even have a group WIS/INT boost song... guess it would be good for group Skill working... =P<br><br>Another guess is that WIS may have a factor with the med rate... but, my bard is the only character I play and I am not to familliar with how caster classes work in their INT/WIS factors... =P<br><br>Echosong<br>Minstrel of the 51st song<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
